<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīmatpāṇḍya
<lb n="2" break="no"/>cakravartti bhujabaḷavīra
<lb n="3"/>kaviyāḷpēṁdradēvara vijayarā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>jyamuttarōttarābhivriddhiprava
<lb n="5" break="no"/>rddhamānamācaṁdrārkkatāraṁbaraṁ sa
<lb n="6" break="no"/>luttamiralu sakavarṣa 1071 bhāva
<lb n="7" break="no"/>saṁvatsarada dhanumāsa sanda saṁkramā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṇadandu hosapaṭṭaṇa basurepuradha
<lb n="9"/>nakharēśvaradēvara sannidhānadalu
<lb n="10"/>samastanakharamuṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> meyu A
<lb n="11"/>lliya nelanuṁ kūḍiralu maunayō 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>giyaru geyda dharmmamappudu dēvara ni
<lb n="13" break="no"/>vēdyakāladoḷu pātrakkaṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> rā
<lb n="14" break="no"/>triya nivēdyakkaṁ koṭṭa pāṇḍyara <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> Iṁ
<lb n="15" break="no"/>tīyartthakkaṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> gāṟara <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> <unclear>gojeya manneya</unclear>
<lb n="16" break="no"/>ra nikki navilu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> biḍāruvāraviṁtī
<lb n="17"/>dharmmamanaḻivanōrvva <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> pātakanige vā
<lb n="18" break="no"/>raṇāsiyoḷu sahasra kavileyaṁ konda
<lb n="19"/>pātakara gatige salguṁ maṁgaḷa mahāśrī ©
</p>

